teline. After which each&#10;tag 'group' is separated by a whiteline.&#10;&#10;@static&#10;&#10;@param ArrayObject $object Ideally.&#10;&#10;@return string" ilk="function" line="81" lineend="83" name="IdealDocBlock" returns="string" signature="string IdealDocBlock(ArrayObject $object)"><variable citdl="ArrayObject" ilk="argument" line="81" name="object" /></scope><scope attributes="public static" doc="This docblock is invalid because the short description 'does not end'&#10;@static&#10;@param ArrayObject $object&#10;@return string" ilk="function" line="91" lineend="97" name="DocBlockWithInvalidShortDescription" returns="string" signature="string DocBlockWithInvalidShortDescription(ArrayObject $object)"><variable citdl="ArrayObject" ilk="argument" line="91" name="object" /></scope><scope attributes="public static" doc="This DocBlock tests whether the @link tag is correctly taken and shown.&#10;&#10;@link http://www.phpdoc.org&#10;&#10;@return void" ilk="function" line="106" lineend="109" name="DocBlockWithLinkTag" signature="void DocBlockWithLinkTag()" /><scope attributes="public static" doc="This tests whether a custom tag with hypen is interpreted&#10;&#10;@custom-tag This is a custom tag&#10;&#10;@return void" ilk="function" line="118" lineend="121" name="DocBlockWithTagWithHyphen" signature="void DocBlockWithTagWithHyphen()" /><scope attributes="public static" doc="This docblock will contain an inline tag to test whether it still crashes.&#10;&#10;This is a test {@link} with an inline tag.&#10;&#10;@static&#10;&#10;@return void" ilk="function" line="132" lineend="135" name="DocBlockWithInlineTag" signature="void DocBlockWithInlineTag()" /></scope></scope>